---
title: Chalet-Style Chicken Dinner with Shallot Gravy and Creamy Mash
description: Tender chicken breasts get the ultimate Canadian treatment tonight with a chalet-style dry rub and savoury shallot gravy! It's only fair to serve up this main with equally cozy sides. Creamy mashed potatoes and crunchy green beans are the perfect accompaniments.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chalet-style-chicken-dinner-5977b096.jpg
